---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Submit an Organization
permalink: /submit/
---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-8">
  <header class="space-y-2">
    <h1 class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
      <i aria-hidden="true" class="fa-solid fa-paper-plane text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100"></i>
      <span>Submit an organization</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">If you know a Calgary-based community group that should be in the directory (or you want to correct an existing listing), you can submit it here.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="prose max-w-none">
    <h2>Guidelines</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Keep it factual</strong>: a short description + contact info is best.</li>
      <li><strong>Include a primary link</strong>: website is ideal; otherwise a social profile.</li>
      <li><strong>Pick one type</strong>: choose the closest match.</li>
      <li><strong>Pick 1–3 interests</strong>: use the existing interest tags where possible.</li>
      <li><strong>Don’t share private info</strong>: only public contact details.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Types</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><code>club</code></li>
      <li><code>activist-group</code></li>
      <li><code>grassroots-initiative</code></li>
      <li><code>resource</code></li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Interests</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><code>anti-racism</code></li>
      <li><code>arts-culture</code></li>
      <li><code>education</code></li>
      <li><code>environment</code></li>
      <li><code>events</code></li>
      <li><code>health-wellness</code></li>
      <li><code>hobby</code></li>
      <li><code>lgbtq2s</code></li>
      <li><code>rec</code></li>
      <li><code>social-impact</code></li>
      <li><code>sports-rec</code></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm dark:border-brand-cyan/30 dark:bg-slate-800 sm:p-6">
    <div class="space-y-1">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Submission form</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Submissions go to our Netlify form inbox. We review and add listings as time permits.</p>
    </div>

    <form name="submit-organization" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" action="/submit/success/" class="mt-6 space-y-6">
      <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="submit-organization" />
      <p class="hidden">
        <label>Don’t fill this out if you’re human: <input name="bot-field" /></label>
      </p>

      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100" for="org_name">Organization name</label>
          <input id="org_name" name="org_name" type="text" required class="w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:border-brand-orange focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-orange/20 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:focus:border-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/20" />
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-1">
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100" for="website">Website (or primary link)</label>
          <input id="website" name="website" type="url" placeholder="https://…" class="w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:border-brand-orange focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-orange/20 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:focus:border-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/20" />
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-1">
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100" for="email">Public contact email (optional)</label>
          <input id="email" name="email" type="email" placeholder="hello@…" class="w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:border-brand-orange focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-orange/20 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:focus:border-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/20" />
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-1">
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100" for="submitter_email">Your email (optional)</label>
          <input id="submitter_email" name="submitter_email" type="email" placeholder="so we can follow up" class="w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:border-brand-orange focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-orange/20 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:focus:border-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/20" />
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-1">
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100" for="type">Type</label>
          <select id="type" name="type" required class="w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:border-brand-orange focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-orange/20 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:focus:border-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/20">
            <option value="">Select…</option>
            <option value="club">club</option>
            <option value="activist-group">activist-group</option>
            <option value="grassroots-initiative">grassroots-initiative</option>
            <option value="resource">resource</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-1">
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100" for="meeting_format">Meeting format (optional)</label>
          <select id="meeting_format" name="meeting_format" class="w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:border-brand-orange focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-orange/20 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:focus:border-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/20">
            <option value="">Any / unknown</option>
            <option value="in-person">in-person</option>
            <option value="hybrid">hybrid</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-1">
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100" for="age_range">Age range (optional)</label>
          <select id="age_range" name="age_range" class="w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:border-brand-orange focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-orange/20 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:focus:border-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/20">
            <option value="">Any / unknown</option>
            <option value="all-ages">all-ages</option>
            <option value="youth">youth</option>
            <option value="seniors">seniors</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-1">
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100" for="location_area">Location area (optional)</label>
          <input id="location_area" name="location_area" type="text" placeholder="e.g., city-wide, downtown" class="w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:border-brand-orange focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-orange/20 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:focus:border-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/20" />
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-1">
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100" for="status">Status (optional)</label>
          <select id="status" name="status" class="w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:border-brand-orange focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-orange/20 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:focus:border-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/20">
            <option value="">Unknown</option>
            <option value="active">active</option>
            <option value="inactive">inactive</option>
            <option value="unknown">unknown</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 pt-6">
          <input id="identity_focused" name="identity_focused" type="checkbox" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-slate-300 text-brand-orange focus:ring-brand-orange/50 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/50" />
          <label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100" for="identity_focused">Identity-focused</label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <fieldset class="space-y-2">
        <legend class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Interests (pick up to 3)</legend>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 text-sm sm:grid-cols-2">
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2"><input type="checkbox" name="interests" value="anti-racism" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-slate-300 text-brand-orange focus:ring-brand-orange/50 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/50" /> anti-racism</label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2"><input type="checkbox" name="interests" value="arts-culture" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-slate-300 text-brand-orange focus:ring-brand-orange/50 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/50" /> arts-culture</label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2"><input type="checkbox" name="interests" value="education" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-slate-300 text-brand-orange focus:ring-brand-orange/50 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/50" /> education</label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2"><input type="checkbox" name="interests" value="environment" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-slate-300 text-brand-orange focus:ring-brand-orange/50 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/50" /> environment</label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2"><input type="checkbox" name="interests" value="events" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-slate-300 text-brand-orange focus:ring-brand-orange/50 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/50" /> events</label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2"><input type="checkbox" name="interests" value="health-wellness" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-slate-300 text-brand-orange focus:ring-brand-orange/50 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/50" /> health-wellness</label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2"><input type="checkbox" name="interests" value="hobby" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-slate-300 text-brand-orange focus:ring-brand-orange/50 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/50" /> hobby</label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2"><input type="checkbox" name="interests" value="lgbtq2s" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-slate-300 text-brand-orange focus:ring-brand-orange/50 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/50" /> lgbtq2s</label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2"><input type="checkbox" name="interests" value="rec" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-slate-300 text-brand-orange focus:ring-brand-orange/50 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/50" /> rec</label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2"><input type="checkbox" name="interests" value="social-impact" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-slate-300 text-brand-orange focus:ring-brand-orange/50 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/50" /> social-impact</label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2"><input type="checkbox" name="interests" value="sports-rec" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-slate-300 text-brand-orange focus:ring-brand-orange/50 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/50" /> sports-rec</label>
        </div>
      </fieldset>

      <div class="space-y-1">
        <label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100" for="description">Short description</label>
        <textarea id="description" name="description" rows="5" required class="w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:border-brand-orange focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-orange/20 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:focus:border-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/20" placeholder="What does this organization do? Who is it for? What should someone know before reaching out?"></textarea>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-1">
        <label class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100" for="notes">Notes (optional)</label>
        <textarea id="notes" name="notes" rows="4" class="w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:border-brand-orange focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-orange/20 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-slate-100 dark:focus:border-brand-cyan dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/20" placeholder="Anything else we should know?"></textarea>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-2">
        <button type="submit" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-slate-900 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-slate-800 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-orange/50 dark:bg-brand-cyan dark:text-slate-900 dark:hover:bg-cyan-500 dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/50">Submit</button>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Prefer email? Send details to <a class="font-medium text-slate-900 hover:underline focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-orange/50 dark:text-cyan-400 dark:focus:ring-brand-cyan/50" href="mailto:calgary@berryhouse.ca">calgary@berryhouse.ca</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>

  <div class="prose max-w-none">
    <h2>If you want to contribute via GitHub</h2>
    <p>If you’d rather add the listing directly, you can create a new Markdown file in <code>src/content/organizations/</code>.</p>

    <p>Template:</p>
    <pre><code>---
layout: layouts/organization.njk
name: "Organization Name"
type: "club" # club, activist-group, grassroots-initiative, resource
interests: ["arts-culture", "social-impact"]
age_range: "all-ages" # all-ages, youth, adults, seniors
identity_focused: false
meeting_format: "in-person" # in-person, hybrid
location_area: "city-wide"
status: "active" # active, inactive, unknown
permalink: "/organizations/{{ page.fileSlug }}/"
---

One-paragraph description.

**Contact Info:**
- Website: https://example.com
- Email: contact@example.com
</code></pre>
  </div>
</section>
